Kathleen Chalfant https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kathleen_Chalfant 0 Kathleen Ann Chalfant (née Bishop; born January 14, 1945) is an American actress. She has appeared in many stage plays, both on Broaway and Off-Broadway, as well as making guest appearances on television series, including the Law Order franchise.
